            "id": 5930438,
            "title": "〈台股盤後〉國安基金神隱？續崩1068點創第3大跌點 3天跌幅17.5%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>國安基金今 (9) 日銀彈上膛伺機護盤，不過，美股三大指數期貨今 (9) 日早盤再度走弱，台股也難獨善其身，呈現開低走低，一路重挫跌破 1 萬 8 千點，最低點下探 17306 點，終場收在 17391.76 點，跌幅為 1068.19 點，改寫歷史第三跌點紀錄，並創下 15 個月來新低，成交量高達 5666 億元。累計本周以來的 3 個交易日下跌 3715.61 點，跌幅達 17.45%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>自美國總統川普宣布關稅以來，全球股市風雲變色，台股也難逃賣壓空襲，今天跌到 173064 點，退到 1 萬 7 與 5 年線支撐；台股今日上市櫃仍一片綠油油，下跌家數有 1800 家，當中有近半、約莫 900 家亮燈跌停，上漲家數僅有 50 家。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>權值股普遍走弱，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSM-US</a>) 今最低下探 780 元，市值僅剩<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a> 20 兆元，終場收在 785 元，跌幅近 4%，聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 下跌近 6%，創下半年多來低點，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 爆出 35.78 萬張大量亮燈跌停，收在 112.5 元，距離去年 10 月下旬的高點 221.5 元幾乎腰斬。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>金控雙雄富邦金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2881:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2881\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2881-TW</a>)、國泰金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2882:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2882\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2882-TW</a>) 雙雙重挫 8% 左右，台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>)、廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 跌幅至少半根以上，封測龍頭日月光投控 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>)、長榮 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2603:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2603\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2603-TW</a>) 也同步亮燈跌停。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>高價股今日再度成為提款機，股王信驊 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5274:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5274\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5274-TW</a>) 跌幅達 7%，其他如世芯 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3661:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3661\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3661-TW</a>)、祥碩 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5269:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5269\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5269-TW</a>)、川湖 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2059:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2059\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2059-TW</a>)、旭隼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6409:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6409\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6409-TW</a>)、嘉澤 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3533:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3533\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3533-TW</a>)、印能科技 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:7734:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7734\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7734-TW</a>)、健策 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3653:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3653\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3653-TW</a>) 皆全數亮燈。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
